{{: Powerup definition}}

'''PowerBuddha''' gives the effect of the {{c|{{CCMD|D|buddha}}}} cheat: the owner of this powerup can still receive damage (in contrast to {{class|PowerInvulnerable}}), but their health can't be reduced below 1, preventing death.

=== [[ZScript]] definition ===
{{ZScriptDefinitionNote|actors/inventory/powerups.zs}}
<syntaxhighlight lang="csharp">
class PowerBuddha : Powerup
{
	Default
	{
		Powerup.Duration -60;
	}
}
</syntaxhighlight>

